metadata.description: MERRY MINTMAS EVERYBODY!! This month I had this crazy idea to make 25 songs in as many days and drop them here on sound. Everyone on this platform has made me feel so welcome and helped me sell out every single drop I've put out so far and for that I am so grateful. This song marks the end of Mintmas and honestly I'm just so proud of myself and my team for making this happen so this one's about putting your mind to something and achieving what you set out to do. Thank you all for being on this journey with me and I look forward to putting in my time here and growing together with all of you guys!
metadata.name: WE DID IT! #1
metadata.title: WE DID IT!
